#12100
doctor 108~
108 Doctor~
A doctor stands here, ready to treat your wounds.
~
This man is a professionally trained doctor.  He works for the 108 Dragons
in the submarine to treat them for injuries they receive in combat.  He
wears glasses, and has green surgical scrubs on.  He cares little about
battles and other such things, but only about treating his patients, and
their survival.
~
human~
