breaston MDS healer~
Dr. Breaston~
Dr. Breaston stands here patiently.
~
Dr. Breaston stands quietly here. He is dressed in a dirty lab coat and
wears a pair of small round glasses. The look in his eyes behind these
lenses is that of one quite mad, having been on an infernal long quest
to make the perfect killing machine.
