old man shinobi~
Old Man~
An old man sits here cross legged waiting to help injured Shinobi.
~
This man is ancient indeed.  His head is almost completely bald, and
is bowed in complete meditation.  He is thouroughly a humble man, with
meager clothes and only necessary possesions.  He sits here waiting to
tend the wounds of all Shinobi who have been injured in combat.
~
