nakei~
Nakei~
Nakei stands here with a grim look upon his face.
~
Standing here in a dark Kimono and a conical hat upon his head, Nakei
eyes you suspiciously.  His eyes glow a deep red, accented by the asian
slant in his brow.  He stands with his muscle packed shoulders and arms
clenched in ready-stance to train those memebers of Judge who are in need
of their skills to be advanced.  He has a Katana strapped across his back
in the ancient style of holding it, ready to attack all who have escaped
their `8Judgement`7.
~
