After meandering through the small hole in the wall to your west, 
you finally arrive inside this secluded corner of the factory. Pipes
that drip constantly surround you, the water pooling on the floor in
some areas and being absorbed by the crumbling walls in others. A 
large portion of this room is dedicated to boxes of ammunition, weapons,
equipment, and other miscellaneous items, along with several tables 
covered with nuts, bolts, and other parts. Overall, it looks like a 
heavily-used workshop.
